<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Villa Sonneville – Confirmation</title>

  <!-- Montserrat -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:200,300,400,500,600" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f3f3f3;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .wrapper {
      padding: 90px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 70px 55px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #e2e2e2;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 55px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: #111111;
    }

    .divider {
      width: 55px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #c8a96a;
      margin: 0 auto 35px auto;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .text {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 28px;
      font-weight: 300;
      text-align: center;
      color: #444444;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .signature {
      margin-top: 35px;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #111111;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    }

    .button-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 35px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      background: #c8a96a;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background: #b8955a;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 50px 28px;
      }
      .title {
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      .text {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="title">Votre inscription est confirmée</div>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="text">
        Merci pour votre inscription à notre lettre d'information.<br><br>
        Vous recevrez désormais les actualités, annonces et événements de Villa Sonneville.
      </div>

      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="./" class="button">Retour au site</a>
      </div>

      <div class="signature">
        Villa Sonneville
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
